              <strong>AKC Standards</strong>
              <span>All parent dogs AKC registered &amp; tested</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="value-item">
            <div class="value-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="value-text">
              <strong>Veterinary Care</strong>
              <span>Full vet records &amp; health guarantees</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="value-item">
            <div class="value-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M21 8.25c0-2.485-2.099-4.5-4.688-4.5-1.935 0-3.597 1.126-4.312 2.733-.715-1.607-2.377-2.733-4.313-2.733C5.1 3.75 3 5.765 3 8.25c0 7.22 9 12 9 12s9-4.78 9-12z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="value-text">
              <strong>Lifelong Support</strong>
              <span>We're here for you long after adoption</span>
